item.title: Theme Features
item.dc:creator: leanthemesdemo
item.content:encoded:
The Kickstart theme also includes the following features.

Slider Optional

Use the free Genesis Responsive Slider plugin to display a slider on the homepage of your Kickstart powered site, or, if you prefer something a little more focused, use a single strong image and text box.

Colour Picker

Don't like red? Or just want to experiment with a different colour? Change Kickstart's primary colour (without any coding) via the colour picker in the WordPress customiser.

Blog Featured Section

Want to highlight a particular article or category? Just enable the Blog Top widget area and make one post stand out at the top of your blog.

Plugin Support

Kickstart is already styled to work well with the popular WordPress plugins Gravity Forms and Testimonials by WooThemes.

Pricing Page & Pricing Table

Stylishly show off a range of pricing options and plans with a dedicated pricing page and a beautifully styled pricing table.

Location Map

If you're a bricks and mortar business (or just want to show off your location) just use the special Google Map friendly widget area on the Contact page template to allow Kickstart to show your startup's location.

Background Image Support

Add a striking full width image to the top of any regular WordPress page (excluding posts or special page templates) simply by adding a Featured Image to the page you want to use.

Post Formats

As well as standard WordPress posts, Kickstart is styled to support Aside, Quote and Status post formats.
